<section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-900">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Section 1: What we do -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">
        What we do
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We support the systems and processes that keep businesses running.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        This can include organizing information, maintaining workflows, and ensuring that day-to-day operations remain consistent and reliable.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2: How we work -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">
        How we work
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We work alongside existing operations on an ongoing basis.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Rather than replacing internal processes, we help maintain and support the systems already in place — making them easier to manage and more dependable over time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3: Our approach -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">
        Our approach
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We focus on clarity, structure, and consistency.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Our role is to support how work is handled behind the scenes so that teams can focus on execution without needing to manage the underlying systems.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-800">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-12">
      Types of work we support
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-12">

      <!-- Block 1: Design and documentation support -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4">Design and documentation support</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          We assist with work that requires structured output, including proposals, layouts, documentation, and supporting materials used in day-to-day operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          This work is typically ongoing and aligned with existing workflows.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Block 2: Technical operations and system support -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4">Technical operations and system support</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          We help maintain and organize the systems that support ongoing work.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          This can include managing workflows, organizing information, supporting internal processes, and ensuring systems remain consistent and usable over time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Block 3: System and infrastructure build-outs -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4">System and infrastructure build-outs</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          In some cases, we set up and maintain complete systems where work is received, organized, and processed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          This may include simple web infrastructure, intake systems, and workflows that connect incoming requests through to a defined outcome.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          These systems are maintained over time as part of ongoing operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          For example, a system may capture incoming requests, organize them, and route them through a defined process such as scheduling, documentation, or follow-up.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
